### ==========================================
### SPECIFICATION — CREATE (admin + editor)
### ==========================================

### Create specification COLOR (admin — válido ✅ 201)
POST {{baseUrl}}/specification/ HTTP/1.1
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "specification_constant_id": 1,
    "subcategory_id": {{subcategoryId}}
}

### ==========================================

### Create specification SIZE (editor — válido ✅ 201)
POST {{baseUrl}}/specification/ HTTP/1.1
Authorization: Bearer {{editorToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "specification_constant_id": 2,
    "subcategory_id": {{subcategoryId}}
}

### ==========================================

### Create specification TEXT (admin — válido ✅ 201)
POST {{baseUrl}}/specification/ HTTP/1.1
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "specification_constant_id": 3,
    "subcategory_id": {{subcategoryId}}
}

### ==========================================

### Create specification (customer — 403 ❌)
POST {{baseUrl}}/specification/ HTTP/1.1
Authorization: Bearer {{customerToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "specification_constant_id": 1,
    "subcategory_id": {{subcategoryId}}
}

### ==========================================

### Create specification (sin token — 401 ❌)
POST {{baseUrl}}/specification/ HTTP/1.1
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "specification_constant_id": 1,
    "subcategory_id": {{subcategoryId}}
}

### ==========================================

### Create specification (constant_id inválido — 422 ❌)
POST {{baseUrl}}/specification/ HTTP/1.1
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "specification_constant_id": 99,
    "subcategory_id": {{subcategoryId}}
}


### ==========================================
### SPECIFICATION VALUE — CREATE (admin + editor)
### ==========================================

### Create spec value NEGRO (admin — válido ✅ 201)
POST {{baseUrl}}/specification/value HTTP/1.1
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "value": "NEGRO",
    "specification_id": {{specId}}
}

### ==========================================

### Create spec value SIZE 32 (editor — válido ✅ 201)
POST {{baseUrl}}/specification/value HTTP/1.1
Authorization: Bearer {{editorToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "value": "32",
    "specification_id": 2
}

### ==========================================

### Create spec value TEXT (admin — válido ✅ 201)
POST {{baseUrl}}/specification/value HTTP/1.1
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "value": "Material: Drill",
    "specification_id": 3
}

### ==========================================

### Create spec value (customer — 403 ❌)
POST {{baseUrl}}/specification/value HTTP/1.1
Authorization: Bearer {{customerToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "value": "ROJO",
    "specification_id": {{specId}}
}

### ==========================================

### Create spec value (sin token — 401 ❌)
POST {{baseUrl}}/specification/value HTTP/1.1
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "value": "ROJO",
    "specification_id": {{specId}}
}

### ==========================================

### Create spec value (specification no existe — 404 ❌)
POST {{baseUrl}}/specification/value HTTP/1.1
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "value": "ROJO",
    "specification_id": 999
}


### ==========================================
### SPECIFICATION — ACTIVATE / DEACTIVATE (admin + editor)
### ==========================================

### Activate specification (admin — válido ✅)
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/specification/{{specId}}/activate HTTP/1.1
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

### ==========================================

### Activate specification (editor — válido ✅)
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/specification/{{specId}}/activate HTTP/1.1
Authorization: Bearer {{editorToken}}

### ==========================================

### Activate specification (customer — 403 ❌)
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/specification/{{specId}}/activate HTTP/1.1
Authorization: Bearer {{customerToken}}

### ==========================================

### Activate specification (sin token — 401 ❌)
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/specification/{{specId}}/activate HTTP/1.1

### ==========================================

### Deactivate specification (admin — válido ✅)
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/specification/{{specId}}/deactivate HTTP/1.1
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

### ==========================================

### Deactivate specification (editor — válido ✅)
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/specification/{{specId}}/deactivate HTTP/1.1
Authorization: Bearer {{editorToken}}

### ==========================================

### Deactivate specification (customer — 403 ❌)
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/specification/{{specId}}/deactivate HTTP/1.1
Authorization: Bearer {{customerToken}}

### ==========================================

### Deactivate specification (sin token — 401 ❌)
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/specification/{{specId}}/deactivate HTTP/1.1


### ==========================================
### SPECIFICATION VALUE — ACTIVATE / DEACTIVATE (admin + editor)
### ==========================================

### Activate spec value (admin — válido ✅)
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/specification/value/{{specValueId}}/activate HTTP/1.1
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

### ==========================================

### Activate spec value (editor — válido ✅)
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/specification/value/{{specValueId}}/activate HTTP/1.1
Authorization: Bearer {{editorToken}}

