### Activate spec value (customer — 403 ❌)
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/specification/value/{{specValueId}}/activate HTTP/1.1
Authorization: Bearer {{customerToken}}

### ==========================================

### Activate spec value (sin token — 401 ❌)
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/specification/value/{{specValueId}}/activate HTTP/1.1

### ==========================================

### Deactivate spec value (admin — válido ✅)
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/specification/value/{{specValueId}}/deactivate HTTP/1.1
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

### ==========================================

### Deactivate spec value (editor — válido ✅)
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/specification/value/{{specValueId}}/deactivate HTTP/1.1
Authorization: Bearer {{editorToken}}

### ==========================================

### Deactivate spec value (customer — 403 ❌)
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/specification/value/{{specValueId}}/deactivate HTTP/1.1
Authorization: Bearer {{customerToken}}

### ==========================================

### Deactivate spec value (sin token — 401 ❌)
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/specification/value/{{specValueId}}/deactivate HTTP/1.1